<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Respon Permintaan</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f6f9;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column; /* To stack card and footer */
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        .card {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
            padding: 40px;
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 450px;
            width: 100%;
        }
        .logo {
            max-width: 150px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .icon {
            font-size: 48px;
            line-height: 1;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            color: #1f2937;
        }
        p {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 0; /* Remove bottom margin to keep card tight */
            color: #4b5563;
        }
        .footer {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #888;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <% if (status === 'success') { %>
        <% if (type === 'approve') { %>
            <div class="card" style="border-top: 5px solid #28a745;">
                <img src="https://logos-world.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Alfamart-Emblem.png" alt="Logo Perusahaan" class="logo">
                <div class="icon" style="color: #28a745;">✓</div>
                <h1>Persetujuan Berhasil</h1>
                <p>Anda telah menyetujui permintaan untuk Nomor Ulok <strong><%= ulok %></strong>. Notifikasi telah dikirimkan.</p>
            </div>
        <% } else { %>
            <div class="card" style="border-top: 5px solid #d9534f;">
                <img src="https://logos-world.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Alfamart-Emblem.png" alt="Logo Perusahaan" class="logo">
                <div class="icon" style="color: #d9534f;">✗</div>
                <h1>Penolakan Terkirim</h1>
                <p>Anda telah menolak permintaan untuk Nomor Ulok <strong><%= ulok %></strong>. Notifikasi telah dikirimkan.</p>
            </div>
        <% } %>
    <% } else { %>
        <div class="card" style="border-top: 5px solid #ffc107;">
            <img src="https://logos-world.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Alfamart-Emblem.png" alt="Logo Perusahaan" class="logo">
            <div class="icon" style="color: #ffc107;">⚠️</div>
            <h1>Gagal atau Sudah Diproses</h1>
            <p><%= msg || 'Permintaan ini mungkin sudah direspon sebelumnya atau terjadi kesalahan.' %></p>
        </div>
    <% } %>
    <div class="footer">Anda bisa menutup halaman ini.</div>
</body>
</html>